g.text: Salesforce is all about relationships, Loom helps organiza-tions leverage that data.By visualizing 5+ degrees of relationships between standard and custom Salesforce objects, you will be able to identify gaps and unknown opportunities that exist for your organiza-tion. Loom’s customizable interface lets users create Loom Views for different use cases of the application, such as fun-raising, recruitment, and sales; search for points of connection within a network map; and filter on pre-existing fields in Salesforce.
Salesforce native network visualization tool that helps organizations identify strategies for engagement.

text.tspan: 1. Visualize all connections - (Any object) up to 10

g.text: Understanding networks is valuable in most industries and functions•Fundraising - 70% of new donors are recruited by current donors.•Recruitment - 70% of jobs are who you know.•Government - who ran against who is important for compliance.•Education - many kids are in multiple households, alumni work at employers (engage them!).•Many others...
